I appreciate your efforts, however, 
having an over-dubbed narrated norwegian male voice on top of the original spoken language is just annoying & unwatchable. 
You should have made it optional. 
Having it optional, it would've been nice 
if you could have had an English subtitle
along with the norwegian one supplied. 
If given the choice, I can't imagine 
how anybody of norwegian descent
would want to watch this, with a 
dubbed narrator, over the subtitle option anyway; "movie blashpemy". 
Thanks anyway though! If you can 
upload the original czechoslovakian 
version with/without optional subtitles, 
it would be appreciated. 
I'm pretty sure it's possible to 
track down a subtitle .srt somewhere.
